WEBVTT

1
00:11:01.547 --> 00:11:05.847 
就这事 我最终还是说服了我妻子
...so I finally just convinced my wife this just made the most sense.

2
00:11:06.719 --> 00:11:08.744 
- 她不想吃冰淇淋? - 谁?
-She didn't want ice cream? -Who?

3
00:11:08.921 --> 00:11:12.482 
哦 我妻子 不
Oh, my wife. No.

4
00:11:12.658 --> 00:11:15.126 
不 实际上她一个人去旅行了
No, actually she's on vacation herself.

5
00:11:15.294 --> 00:11:17.888 
白羊 白羊 白羊
White sheep, white sheep, white sheep.

6
00:11:18.063 --> 00:11:21.396 
- 很难一起去旅行 - 白羊
-It's difficult to take trips together. -White sheep.

7
00:11:22.167 --> 00:11:25.136 
没事 我们好好的
It's fine. We make it work.

8
00:11:26.538 --> 00:11:28.529 
我在前面往左下车
I'm up here on the left.

